27F6DBFD.Line7.789BF: I don’t know…but I will try.

C1EB557F.Line9.789BF: If you are still willing to join me, stare into the flames. Let them carry you into my memories…

F40DE8F9.Line3.789BF: You should know that this ritual will be dangerous for both of us.
